subSubSection.paragraph:
By almost all its dimensions, the 

P. lindermayeri

from Hadjidimovo-1 is larger than that of Pikermi. This is especially true of teeth and horn dimensions, and brain case size (
Table 1
; 
Figs 3-5
).
